 꼭꼭 챙겨주세요.​ ​ ​ 자, 이렇게 해서 간단한 후식까지 구성한 수능 도시락이 완성되었어요~ 예쁜 도시락 통에 담아주니 영양 가득한 엄마표 브라이트댁 수능 도시락이 한껏 더 정성 가득해 보이지 않으신가요?       수능을 앞둔 수험생 자녀들에게 그 동안의 노력은 배신하지 않을 거라는 ﻿  용기와 격려를 팍팍! 주시길 바랄게요. ^^ 엄마의 정성과 염원이 가득 담긴 수능 도시락을 만들어 준다면 수험생들도 분명 그에 보답하는 최상의 실력과 컨디션을 발휘할거라 믿습니다~ 브라이트댁도 전국에 있는 모든 수험생들과 가족 여러분들을 응원합니다~~!! ​ ​ ​","images":["http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141108_179/3mhappyhouse_1415458714513uaJsD_JPEG/%BC%F6%B4%C9_%B5%B5%BD%C3%B6%F4_%B8%B8%B5%E9%B1%E2_1_%BD%E6%B3%D7%C0%CF.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141108_191/3mhappyhouse_1415458714845xc35h_JPEG/%BC%F6%B4%C9_%B5%B5%BD%C3%B6%F4_%B8%B8%B5%E9%B1%E2_2.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141108_83/3mhappyhouse_1415458715137AxKGd_JPEG/%BC%F6%B4%C9_%B5%B5%BD%C3%B6%F4_%B8%B8%B5%E9%B1%E2_3.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141108_283/3mhappyhouse_1415458715434wWBC9_JPEG/%BC%F6%B4%C9_%B5%B5%BD%C3%B6%F4_%B8%B8%B5%E9%B1%E2_4.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141108_186/3mhappyhouse_1415458715743D4Ev5_JPEG/%BC%F6%B4%C9_%B5%B5%BD%C3%B6%F4_%B8%B8%B5%E9%B1%E2_5.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141108_156/3mhappyhouse_1415458716146qPli8_JPEG/%BC%F6%B4%C9_%B5%B5%BD%C3%B6%F4_%B8%B8%B5%E9%B1%E2_6.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141108_166/3mhappyhouse_1415458716451CYyLp_JPEG/%BC%F6%B4%C9_%B5%B5%BD%C3%B6%F4_%B8%B8%B5%E9%B1%E2_7.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141108_293/3mhappyhouse_1415458716818hnBIR_JPEG/%BC%F6%B4%C9_%B5%B5%BD%C3%B6%F4_%B8%B8%B5%E9%B1%E2_8.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141108_224/3mhappyhouse_1415458717104sWeO6_JPEG/%BC%F6%B4%C9_%B5%B5%BD%C3%B6%F4_%B8%B8%B5%E9%B1%E2_9.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141108_216/3mhappyhouse_1415458717391omQqz_JPEG/%BC%F6%B4%C9_%B5%B5%BD%C3%B6%F4_%B8%B8%B5%E9%B1%E2_10.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141108_10/3mhappyhouse_1415458717707uzJFw_JPEG/%BC%F6%B4%C9_%B5%B5%BD%C3%B6%F4_%B8%B8%B5%E9%B1%E2_11.jpg?type=","http